Local travel company Aslan Adventure has partnered with Europamundo, one of the largest tour operators in the world, to open up the world to Kenya. They celebrated the partnership at the Movenpick Hotel on September 18. Europamundo Vacations is one of the largest coach tour operators in the world affiliated to the United Nations World Tourism Organisation. The partnership is expected to increase the number of travellers to and from the country and will greatly boost its economy. Present were the Europamundo Vacaciones tour manager Javier Villodre and Aslan Adventures Tours and Travel MD Neena Jabbala.